#chown
#chown user.group /directory/path 

chown aws.devops /opt/webdata

#symbolic method to change permission modes
chmod u+rwx /directory/path 

#numeric method u = rwx, g = rw- o = ---
chmod 760 /directory/path 

#sudoers
If user does not want to enter its password after running sudo command then
Add NOPASSWD option in users entry in sudoers file as follows:
username ALL=(ALL:ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL



